reviewText:
I was so thrilled to find this.....and excited to view the legendary Dwight Twilley....after years of being a fan!

GOOD THINGS..
great show, great playing, singing and cool filming

BAD THINGS
crappy DVD authoring, cheap packaging...slim dvd case, color copies for art..and a DVD R!!!!

so...proceed with caution..
hopefully a legit company other than Gigatone will get a hold of this and issue it proper!
